 the original Slayaway Camp diehards as well!) we've built upon the brain busting core mechanics of Slayaway Camp with even MORE slaughteriffic new additions like pushable crates and rolling boulders you can use to block or squish your victims with; grass and trees you can interact with to frighten your victims from adjacent spaces; super awesome pressure switches that trigger trap floors and doors and mighty lawnmowers that can run over the campers for some truly grotesque 'manscaping'.<br> <br>Not only that but there are 4 new classes of killers in addition to the traditional 'Slasher' class. Sorcerers can fire projectiles across the levels, destroying obstacles and turning campers into a bloody mist! Beasts let loose a frightening roar to freeze all the campers in place. Monster class killers can create zombie friends from dead campers to help in their slaughter and the special Ghost killers are able to 'phase' through obstacles to surprise slaughter unsuspecting victims!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2737140/extras/21173da84133d3680781d899a645d93a.poster.avif?t=1737750977\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2737140/extras/21173da84133d3680781d899a645d93a.webm?t=1737750977\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2737140/extras/21173da84133d3680781d899a645d93a.mp4?t=1737750977\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
